comments.body:
Hi David - 

Doesn't actually work.  A given excludedSubtree is not mated to any specific permittedSubtree.  The name acceptance logic is something like:

if (excludedSubtrees exist) {
  if (any excludedSubtrees match the name) THEN {
     reject;
  } 
}
if (includedSubtrees exist) {
   if (any includedSubtrees match the name) then {
     accept;
   } 
  reject;
}
accept;

Mike
